{"tid":677310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拍節目過電？蔡思貝笑余德丞仰慕自己","createTime":"2018-05-25T05:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T05:09:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57398dda9f6133cb854a12355729a5e4470662de","tid":677310,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】蔡思貝及余德丞出席《緬甸奇幻旅程》記者會，他們說節目充滿無謂笑話及蝦碌事情，思貝覺得這次旅程有如小學生去旅行，他們首次出埠拍旅遊節目十分難忘，坐勻當地的交通工具，尤其坐私人熱氣球很浪漫，可惜對象是余德丞。<br />\n<br />\n在節目中他們要吃螞蟻，還品嚐皇帝餐及幫襯米芝蓮三星餐館，余德丞指當地的食物較重香料，思貝很多東西也不吃，笑指辛苦他要吃多點。說到宣傳片拍到蔡思貝被異性捉住合照，她戲言與對方已定情，而他們的司機很像劉青雲，又說以前很喜歡看洪永城及黃翠如拍旅遊節目，希望每年拍1次旅遊節目，好想去偏遠地方。<br />\n<br />\n講到思貝出名電力強，問余德丞有沒有過電？思貝笑說對方的頭髮電到攣，又指余德丞出名仰慕她。余德丞則說未入公司已仰慕思貝，思貝亦表示很欣賞余德丞的才華，自對方主持《體育世界》已喜歡，兩人互笠高帽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VQGmgHOBf5eNVw7yzjUycw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180524f165122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVQGmgHOBf5eNVw7yzjUycw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180524f165122.jpg&h=d09f4951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%8D%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E9%81%8E%E9%9B%BB-%E8%94%A1%E6%80%9D%E8%B2%9D%E7%AC%91%E4%BD%99%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%9E%E4%BB%B0%E6%85%95%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1-080800052.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%259B%25BB-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E6%2580%259D%25E8%25B2%259D%25E7%25AC%2591%25E4%25BD%2599%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25B8%259E%25E4%25BB%25B0%25E6%2585%2595%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1-080800052.html&d=ZVrugfLkI%2B5%2F78SZCSYSShv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4c8f099e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%8D%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E9%81%8E%E9%9B%BB-%E8%94%A1%E6%80%9D%E8%B2%9D%E7%AC%91%E4%BD%99%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%9E%E4%BB%B0%E6%85%95%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1-080800052.html</a>"},{"pid":"58bb236575f15dabfc40863b88eacca036011a1c","tid":677310,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/134028_8ff34bf0d191b50482143f3b6e955ea0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F134028_8ff34bf0d191b50482143f3b6e955ea0.png&h=e503bff0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00dfa13929476116393a21c23ac4b3e69f766644","tid":677310,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58bb236575f15dabfc40863b88eacca036011a1c","tid":677310,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/134028_8ff34bf0d191b50482143f3b6e955ea0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F134028_8ff34bf0d191b50482143f3b6e955ea0.png&h=e503bff0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"其實已經唔似<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能經過上次慘痛經歷"},{"pid":"b43aa042c8d11e01dc970662144e6ebf4bbe2b56","tid":677310,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00dfa13929476116393a21c23ac4b3e69f766644","tid":677310,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58bb236575f15dabfc40863b88eacca036011a1c","tid":677310,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/134028_8ff34bf0d191b50482143f3b6e955ea0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F134028_8ff34bf0d191b50482143f3b6e955ea0.png&h=e503bff0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"其實已經唔似<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能經過上次慘痛經歷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:48:21.